h/pytorch/pull/9466.patch"}, "body_html": "<p>Storage views were previously used to implement CUDA IPC sharing,<br>\nbut they weren't necessary.  The new strategy is described in<br>\nNote [CUDA IPC and the caching allocator].</p>\n<p>This also fixes an unrelated bug, where we weren't actually using<br>\nthe Tensor forking pickler, because we didn't register a pickler<br>\nfor torch.Tensor.</p>\n<p><span class=\"issue-keyword tooltipped tooltipped-se\" aria-label=\"This pull request closes issue #9447.\">Fixes</span> <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load issue title\" data-id=\"341249315\" data-permission-text=\"Issue title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/issues/9447\" data-hovercard-type=\"issue\" data-hovercard-url=\"/pytorch/pytorch/issues/9447/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/issues/9447\">#9447</a>.  <span class=\"issue-keyword tooltipped tooltipped-se\" aria-label=\"This pull request closes issue #46.\">Fixes</span> <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load issue title\" data-id=\"178428668\" data-permission-text=\"Issue title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/issues/46\" data-hovercard-type=\"issue\" data-hovercard-url=\"/pytorch/pytorch/issues/46/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/issues/46\">#46</a>.</p>\n<p>Signed-off-by: Edward Z. Yang <a href=\"mailto:ezyang@fb.com\">ezyang@fb.com</a></p>\n<p>CC <a class=\"user-mention\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/hovercards?user_id=4583066\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/apaszke\">@apaszke</a></p>", "body_text": "Storage views were previously used to implement CUDA IPC sharing,\nbut they weren't necessary.  The new strategy is described in\nNote [CUDA IPC and the caching allocator].\nThis also fixes an unrelated bug, where we weren't actually using\nthe Tensor forking pickler, because we didn't register a pickler\nfor torch.Tensor.\nFixes #9447.  Fixes #46.\nSigned-off-by: Edward Z. Yang ezyang@fb.com\nCC @apaszke", "body": "Storage views were previously used to implement CUDA IPC sharing,\r\nbut they weren't necessary.  The new strategy is described in\r\nNote [CUDA IPC and the caching allocator].\r\n\r\nThis also fixes an unrelated bug, where we weren't actually using\r\nthe Tensor forking pickler, because we didn't register a pickler\r\nfor torch.Tensor.\r\n\r\nFixes #9447.  Fixes #46.\r\n\r\nSigned-off-by: Edward Z. Yang <ezyang@fb.com>\r\n\r\nCC @apaszke \r\n\r\n"}